    <p>{`Just like most the mountain’s I’ve ever climbed though, when you finally do get to the top, it appears there is yet another mountain in front of you that is a little bit taller than you. For now that mountain is establishing myself as a professional. And I am happy to say that I can think of no better place to do this at, than the company I have just signed an offer of employment with, `}<a parentName="p" {...{
